As much as I love my smoker, I work full time and love coming home to dinner being ready! That’s where this super easy recipe comes in! 
Fall Off The Bone Ribs
1 rack of baby back ribs 
Dry rub seasoning (I love the Tender Love & Rub from @randrbbq) 
Cut into quarters place in crockpot 
Mix together: 
1 1/2 c ketchup
1 whole onion cut up into large pieces 
I/4 c white vinegar 
1/4 c brown sugar
1 Tbsp dry rub of choice 
1/2 c water
Pour over ribs and cook on low for 8 hrs
Enjoy 😋 
You can purchase these yummy dry rubs for your BBQ lover or yourself at any R&R BBQ restaurant!
